  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IVoidFinder

    public class SubsetSamplingVoidFinder
extends AbstractVoidFinder
    an instance of IVoidFinder that uses a subsection of the AxisIndexer data. Note that the subset indexes are applied to the x and y axes of AxisIndexer data.
